---
title: Katsu Crumbed Chicken & Ginger Rice with Roasted Eggplant & Slaw
description: If you want your kitchen to smell amazing you don’t need to pull out every spice you own, just a simple katsu sauce, ginger rice and roasted eggplant will do. On a golden crumbed chicken, it’s enough to have your senses blissfully overwhelmed with fragrances that leave your mouth watering.
